biography: Destination for bold elegance and style.

latestIgtvVideos.caption:
What exactly makes a Good Girl great? Hear the recipe straight from our divine new crew —@karliekloss, @preciousleexoxo, @ash_foo, @_dilone, and @oliviavinten.

Hint: it’s all about being true to who you are.

#goodgirlcarolinaherrera

What do @karliekloss, @preciousleexoxo, @ash_foo, @_dilone, and @oliviavinten have in common? One — they’re part of our superstar new crew of Good Girls.
Two — they’re fabulous at Chaka Khan karaoke.

Video by @pedro.artola 

#goodgirlcarolinaherrera
Know how to speak fluent Herrera? As you see backstage at our tulle-tastic Fall Winter 2022 show, If you can say the words “bold,” “fearless,” and “fabulous,” then you definitely do.

Recreate @lauren.parsons’ natural yet polished look for @wesgordon’s FW22 runway show.

Start off by applying the Embellishing powder that’s closest to your skin tone. With their weightless second skin texture, they deliver buildable coverage that lasts for hours.

Then, elongate the eyes and frame them with the Fabulous Eyes smudge-proof mascara. Designed to lengthen and lift lashes, the formula is enriched with beautifying white jasmine extract essence to moisturize and condition for fuller, healthier lashes. 

Next, give your lips a natural-looking stain with the blur matte finish lipstick from the Nude Couture collection in the shade Peanut (color n° 781). Providing six hours of long-lasting color, the Herrera Beauty lipsticks are full of hyaluronic filling spheres for fuller looking lips and a creamy melt-in-the-skin texture, making them as conditioning as they are versatile.

Lastly, stain the cheeks using the same Nude Couture lipstick shade and accentuate the high points of the face using the Universal Highlighter for a lit-from-within glow. 

Discover the entire Nude Couture range at carolinaherrera.com and buy online for selected countries.

Featuring the new Nude Couture lipstick collection: 
🤎 10 Shades of Nude 
🎈 Ultra-lightweight formula for a second skin feel
💦 Infused with Hyaluronic filling spheres to blur fine lines
🌱 Contains natural Oryza Sativa Hull powder for a flawless matte look
⏱ Longwearing finish lasts up to 6 hours
🧸 Lips look rejuvenated and feel hydrated for up to 12 hours

For a Fall Winter collection of drama and delight, the ideal purse is an absolute must — this season, our Creative Director @WesGordon has reimagined the Initials Insignia bag with sweet leather bows and the Matryoshka bag with romantic ruffles and beads. 
#CHInsignia #CHInitialsInsignia #CHMartyoshkaBag

How does one celebrate 40 years of style? With precious pink and precocious polka dots and shoulders that poof, with ravishing red and rainbows, rainbows everywhere. For Carolina Herrera’s 40th anniversary, we’re commemorating our iconic house codes — the colors, styles, shapes, and sizes that have defined us. 
Head to CarolinaHerrera.com to experience more of what makes us us.
Video: @chusandgreg
Styling: @albamelendo

MIDNIGHT SPARK by #HerreraBeauty

Defy expectations with the perfect blend of sultry red eyes and a soft, nude lip. Chic Mono Eyeshadows in Shimmer Burgundy 14 and Shimmer Violet 12 create a rich, buildable shimmer that pairs perfectly with the sheer, natural finish of Fabulous Kiss Sheer Lipstick in Nude Smile 140. To finish the look, Fabulous Eyeliner adds definition with a flawless, precise line, while Fabulous Eyes Waterproof Mascara enhances volume and lift.

Ready to shop the look? Head online for selected countries at carolinaherrera.com.
